{
  "number": 5524,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/5524",
  "title": "fix(events): deduplicate equal events",
  "body": "- adds a temporary cache for events\r\n- only the first event of a type is sent (fixing #5442)\r\n- if there's a new result, we send again\r\n- if multiple events happen at the same time (default, and custom), they're only deduplicated when they have the same even type\r\n- a double click or multiple clicks over time still get deduplicated, we could solve this by clearing the cache after a certain timeout _as well_\r\n\r\nFX-2246\r\n\r\nsee also #5460, a previous approach\r\n\r\ndraft because tests aren't updated yet\r\n",
